2020/07/Fahmi-copy-1-75x75.png 75w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Fahmi-copy-1-150x150.png 150w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Fahmi-copy-1-300x300.png 300w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Fahmi-copy-1.png 550w" sizes="(max-width: px) 100vw, px" /></div><div class="testimonial-name">Fahmi Reza</div><div class="testimonial-company"><a href="http://Head of E-Commerce of PT Transmarco Indonesia - Hush Puppies" target="_blank">Head of E-Commerce of PT Transmarco Indonesia - Hush Puppies</a></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial t-slide post-9408"><div class="testimonial-inner"><div class="testimonial-inner-wrap"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>&#8220;Im incredibly impressed with the ICUBE teams ability to put together a comprehensive BRD with supporting screenshots, analysis, and summary with the limited number of hours allocated for this task (A+).&#8221;</p></div><div class="testimonial-client"><div class="testimonial-image"><img   src="https://www.sirclo.com/inc/uploads/2020/07/Ryan-copy-1.png" class="attachment-widget-thumbnail size-widget-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Ryan-copy-1-75x75.png 75w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Ryan-copy-1-150x150.png 150w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Ryan-copy-1-300x300.png 300w, https://sirclo.id:443/file/2020/07/Ryan-copy-1.png 550w" sizes="(max-width: px) 100vw, px" /></div><div class="testimonial-name">Ryan Sheppard</div><div class="testimonial-company"><a href="http://Head of US Operations of Kensium Solutions" target="_blank">Head of US Operations of Kensium Solutions</a></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial t-slide post-9409"><div class="testimonial-inner"><div class="testimonial-inner-wrap"><div class="testimonial-content"><div class="maybe-clear"></div><p>&#8220;NIVEA berhasil masuk di ranah online dan menjadi produk yang populer dengan perin